# AWS (local / optional)
AWS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_12_digit_account_id
DEFAULT_AWS_REGION=us-east-1
PROJECT_NAME=twin

# OpenAI on Lambda: set these in repo-root .env, then ./scripts/deploy.sh (passes -var so it beats terraform.tfvars).
# LLM_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
#
# GitHub Actions: Settings → Secrets → add OPENAI_API_KEY (optional). Repo Variables (optional): LLM_PROVIDER=openai, OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini. Without the secret, deploy uses Bedrock from terraform.tfvars.
